<title>Kasutajaliides</title>
<p>This page explains all options for configuring the User Interface in Preferences in <app>Parabolic</app>.</p>

<terms>
    <item>
        <title>Kujundus</title>
        <p>The theme for the user interface.</p>
        <note style="advanced">
            <p>Default: System</p>
        </note>
    </item>
    <item>
        <title>Keela arvuti uinumine</title>
        <p>Parabolic will prevent the computer from sleeping while downloads are running.</p>
        <note style="advanced">
            <p>Vakimisi: pole kasutusel</p>
        </note>
    </item>
    <item>
        <title>Taasta kokkujooksnud allalaadimised</title>
        <p>Parabolic will recover downloads that were in progress when the app crashed.</p>
        <note style="advanced">
            <p>Default: On</p>
        </note>
    </item>
    <item>
        <title>Laadi alla kohe peale valideerimist</title>
        <p>Parabolic will immediatly download media after validation, without presenting configuration options to the user.</p>
        <note style="advanced">
            <p>Vakimisi: pole kasutusel</p>
        </note>
    </item>
    <item>
        <title>Kirjete vanus allalaadimisete ajaloos</title>
        <p>The amount of time to keep past downloads in the app's history.</p>
        <note style="advanced">
            <p>Default: One Week</p>
        </note>
    </item>
</terms>
